System-based defense facilities have rather specialized uses: shields guard against enemy assaults and bombardments; ion cannons paralyze attacking ships and allow for evacuations while a system is under blockade; laser batteries destroy attacking ships or troops. Having defense facilities in place on each of our key systems will hinder the Rebel Alliance's ability to take our systems by force.  Defense facilities can be built via construction yards to any Imperial-controlled system which possesses enough free energy to support the facilities.